[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue type  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA Denial-of-Service condition is observed: the PDF processing pipeline allocates [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexcessive heap memory while parsing embedded Type [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m font data [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPFB format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, leading[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto an `OutOfMemoryError`. The fuzzer labels this as `FuzzerSecurityIssueLow: Out of[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmemory`.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Observed behavior  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The crash occurs inside `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb` when [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreading PFB segments.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Downstream calls include `Type1Font.createWithPFB`, `PDType1Font.<init>`, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDFontFactory.createFont`, and into PDFBox’s content-stream processing [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`PDFStreamEngine` → `PDFTextStripper`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Complete stack trace highlights the flow from font parsing through text [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstripping, ending at the fuzzer’s `fuzzerTestOneInput`.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key observations  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The failure reproduces under a JVM max-heap setting of approximately [0m[1;36m1710[0m[39m MB [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`-Xmx1710m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The input is a malformed or adversarial PDF that embeds large or ill-formed PFB[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The fuzzer harness simply feeds the input to PDFBox’s text-extraction API; it [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis not the root cause but exposes the underlying issue.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Code areas for investigation  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser` – handling of segment lengths and [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcumulative memory allocation when parsing PFB streams.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. `org.apache.fontbox.type1.Type1Font.createWithPFB` – integration point between[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mraw PFB bytes and the font object model.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. `org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.font.PDType1Font` and `PDFontFactory.createFont` – [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39morchestration of font resource creation.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. `PDResources.getFont` and `PDFStreamEngine.processOperator` – resource lookup [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand operator dispatch.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. `PDFTextStripper.processPage` – overall text-extraction logic that triggers [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfull font parsing for each page.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy reviewing these components, one can assess how PFB data is buffered, validate [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39many size limits, and understand where unbounded memory growth occurs during PDF [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m237[0m[39m:                        byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m segment1 = [0m[1;35mArrays.copyOfRange[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m161[0m[39m:            long newTotal = total + size;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m162[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnewTotal > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m163[0m[39m:                throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"record size would be too large: "[0m[39m + [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnewTotal[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m164[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m165[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m166[0m[39m:            byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m ar = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39msize[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m167[0m[39m:            int got = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[39mar[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m168[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mgot != size[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m169[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m170[0m[39m:                throw new [0m[1;35mEOFException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"EOF while reading PFB font"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m171[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m172[0m[39m:            total += size;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m173[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mtypeList.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecordType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m174[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mbarrList.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mar[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m175[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m176[0m[39m:        while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m177[0m[39m:        [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdmodel/font/PDType1Font.jav[0m[1;92ma:216[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m216[0m[39m:                    byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m bytes = [0m[1;35mfontFile.toByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m217[0m[39m:                    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes.length == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m218[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m219[0m[39m:                        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Font data unavailable"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m220[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m221[0m[39m:                    length1 = [0m[1;35mrepairLength1[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes, length1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m222[0m[39m:                    length2 = [0m[1;35mrepairLength2[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes, length1, length2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m223[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview of the issue  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The root cause of the OOM is the unbounded eager buffering of embedded PFB font [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata in two places:  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m constructor calling `[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m([0m[39mb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m PDType1Font using `[0m[1;35mfontFile.toByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   We need to convert both sides to a streaming‐first approach that enforces the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting MAX_LENGTH cap before any large allocation, while preserving existing font[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing logic and metadata-based length repairs.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. PfbParser streaming refactor  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Add a new constructor and parse method in PfbParser for streaming [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInputStreams:  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Signature: `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException`  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Internally, read segment headers one by one from `in`, exactly as in the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcurrent `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` loop, enforcing `total + size <= MAX_LENGTH` before [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocating each segment’s `byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39msize[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Avoid any pre-buffering of the entire stream; read markers and sizes [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdirectly from `in`.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Retain existing checks for START_MARKER, recordType, and combined total [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - After collecting all segments in memory, proceed with building the font [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobject as before.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Deprecate [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbut keep for backward compatibility[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m the old `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpath; have it delegate to the new streaming logic by wrapping the byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m in a [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mByteArrayInputStream.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Expose a streaming entry point in Type1Font  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Add an overload in `Type1Font`:  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        `public static Type1Font [0m[1;35mcreateWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream pfbStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException`  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – Internally, call the new streaming `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructor.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      – Continue to call the existing private constructors or factory logic that [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuilds the Type1Font from the parsed segments.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Retain the existing `[0m[1;35mcreateWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfbBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method, but modify it to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mforward to the new streaming overload:  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        `return [0m[1;35mcreateWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew [0m[1;35mByteArrayInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Change PDType1Font to use streaming PFB parsing  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In `PDType1Font` around lines [0m[1;36m216[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m227[0m[39m of `PDType1Font.java`:[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Replace the eager `byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m bytes = [0m[1;35mfontFile.toByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; [0m[33m...[0m[39m [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mType1Font.createWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` logic with:  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Obtain a raw InputStream from the COSStream:  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         `InputStream fontStream = [0m[1;35mfontFile.createInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Wrap it in a `BufferedInputStream` and, if needed, a `PushbackInputStream`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto peek the first byte without consuming it.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Read one byte to check for `PFB_START_MARKER`; if matched, `[0m[1;35mreset[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream; otherwise fall back to non-PFB logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., CFF, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Call the new streaming entry point:  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         `t1 = [0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfontStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Remove or guard the old `repairLength1/repairLength2` and `[0m[1;35mtoByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvocations so they only apply to non-PFB cases [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., CFF or Type1C fonts[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Preserve existing functionality  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The streaming parser reproduces exactly the same segment parsing rules [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mmarkers, sizes, type checks, MAX_LENGTH guard[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The public API of `Type1Font` remains unchanged for any existing code calling [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mcreateWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Non-PFB font workflows in `PDType1Font` are untouched; only the PFB path is [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrerouted through streaming.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Potential side effects and mitigation  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure the new InputStream-based constructor handles `[0m[1;35mmark[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[35m/[0m[95mreset[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` properly[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhen peeking the first byte. If the underlying stream does not support mark, wrap [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min `BufferedInputStream` with a sufficient buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39mat least [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m byte[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Double-check error messages and exception types remain consistent so that [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting callers and tests see the same IOException variants.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run the full PDFBox test suite [0m[1;39m([0m[39min particular the PDFBOX-[0m[1;36m2607[0m[39m regression [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtests[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to confirm no behavioral changes for valid PFBs or two-segment embedded [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPFBs.[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Streaming parsing enforces the MAX_LENGTH guard before any large allocation, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meliminating the OOM risk.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By providing both byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m and InputStream entry points, we maximize backward [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompatibility and minimize disruption.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This aligns with similar streaming‐first fixes elsewhere in PDFBox [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimage streams, CFF parsing[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No harness or test code is touched; all changes are confined to PfbParser, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1Font, and the PFB branch of PDType1Font.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fix addresses the evaluation report’s recommendation to “avoid preloading [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe entire font” and ensures adversarial inputs cannot exhaust heap via unbounded [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreadAllBytes or toByteArray calls.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== libFuzzer crashing input ==[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe project’s Jazzer-based fuzzing harness triggered an OutOfMemoryError in [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PfbParser.parsePfb`, indicating unbounded heap usage when parsing PFB font data. A[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch was applied in two modules—FontBox [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`PfbParser.java`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and PDFBox [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`PDType1Font.java`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m—to introduce streaming-aware parsing, split full-PFB and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtwo-segment handling, and add size checks. After applying the patch, the FontBox [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmodule failed to compile with four “cannot find symbol” errors for `Files`, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Paths`, and `Arrays` in `PfbParser.java`.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer reported `com.code_intelligence.jazzer.api.FuzzerSecurityIssueLow: Out[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof memory` caused by `java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space`.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack trace shows the failure in `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvoked during PDF text extraction [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvia `PDFTextStripper.getText`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No evidence in the report of external influences; the heap exhaustion occurs [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mduring PFB parsing in FontBox.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.java`: imports of [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`java.io`, `java.nio.file.Files`, `java.nio.file.Paths`, and `java.util.Arrays` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwere rearranged or removed.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdmodel/font/PDType1Font.java`: the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode that read embedded Type [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m font streams was rewritten to  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • detect a PFB start marker in a `BufferedInputStream`  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • use `Type1Font.createWithPFB` for full PFB streams  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • fall back to reading the entire stream as a `byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`, enforcing a maximum [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallowed size [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`PfbParser.MAX_LENGTH`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, repairing `[0m[35m/[0m[95mLength1[0m[39m` and `[0m[35m/[0m[95mLength2[0m[39m`, and [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconcatenating segments via `ByteArrayOutputStream`  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • retain the existing segment-based creation [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`Type1Font.createWithSegments`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m for[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msmall embedded fonts  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The patch introduced new dependencies on `BufferedInputStream`, [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ByteArrayOutputStream`, `Arrays`, and on constants/methods from `PfbParser`.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Result  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Compilation of the FontBox module failed with errors in `PfbParser.java` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m264[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m273[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • cannot find symbol `Files`  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • cannot find symbol `Paths`  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • cannot find symbol `Arrays` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtwice[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- These errors indicate missing imports or incorrect reference scopes for the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclasses used in the patch.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The import block in [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.java`: confirm which [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`java.*` and third-party classes are required [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `java.nio.file.Files`, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`java.nio.file.Paths`, `java.util.Arrays`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and restore or adjust imports [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maccordingly.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The definition and visibility of `PfbParser.MAX_LENGTH` and `PFB_START_MARKER`: [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mensure these constants are defined and accessible.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The new streaming logic in `PDType1Font.java`: verify that the methods [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`repairLength1` and `repairLength2` remain available and correctly handle [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbyte-array inputs.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The integration points where `[0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithSegments[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` are invoked: check for dependency [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchanges in FontBox’s `Type1Font`.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Overall module dependencies in Maven: ensure the FontBox and PDFBox submodules [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msee the same versions of shared classes [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`PfbParser`, `Type1Font`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo assumptions have been made about root causes beyond the visible compilation [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merrors or about possible fixes. The report focuses on documenting the observed [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39missue, the attempted patch, and the resulting build failures.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:90[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m97[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:     * @param filename  the file name[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:     * @throws IOException if an IO-error occurs.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:    public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal String filename[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m95[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mthis[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mFiles.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilename[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:260[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m277[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m260[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m261[0m[39m:     * Returns the first segment[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m262[0m[39m:     * @return first segment bytes[0m                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m264[0m[39m:    public byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;35mgetSegment1[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m265[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m266[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35mArrays.copyOfRange[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbdata, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, lengths[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m267[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m268[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m269[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m270[0m[39m:     * Returns the second segment[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m271[0m[39m:     * @return second segment bytes[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m272[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m273[0m[39m:    public byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;35mgetSegment2[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m274[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m275[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35mArrays.copyOfRange[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbdata, lengths[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, lengths[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m + [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlengths[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m276[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m277[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Restore missing imports in FontBox’s PfbParser.java:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Reintroduce the three imports that were accidentally removed by the last [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch:[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.nio.file.Files;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.nio.file.Paths;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.util.Arrays;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Place them alongside the existing `java.io.*` and `java.util.ArrayList` [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimports so that:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.io.ByteArrayInputStream;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.io.EOFException;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.io.IOException;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.io.InputStream;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.nio.file.Files;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.nio.file.Paths;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.util.ArrayList;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.util.Arrays;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.util.List;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This will resolve the “cannot find symbol” errors for `Files`, `Paths`, and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Arrays` without altering any harness or test code.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Preserve the existing streaming‐aware parsing logic:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The constructor `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString filename[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` uses [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mFiles.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilename[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. Restoring the imports immediately makes [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat code compile as intended.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The segment‐splitting methods `[0m[1;35mgetSegment1[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mgetSegment2[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` rely on [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Arrays.copyOfRange`. Restoring `java.util.Arrays` ensures these methods continue [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto work without rewriting them.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Validate constants and other references:[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm that `PfbParser.MAX_LENGTH` and `PFB_START_MARKER` are still defined [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the class or correctly inherited from the initial codebase. No changes should be[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnecessary unless those constants were inadvertently removed in the earlier patch.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure that the new streaming branch in `PDType1Font.java` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich uses [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Type1Font.createWithPFB`, `repairLength1`, `repairLength2`, and [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ByteArrayOutputStream`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m compiles against the restored PfbParser.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Re-run the Maven build for the FontBox module:[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The restored imports will eliminate the four compilation errors in [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PfbParser.java`.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No other modules, harness code, or test code require changes, preserving [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting fuzzing logic, test suites, and external dependencies.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Minimal invasive change: only re-adds the exact imports needed to satisfy the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompiler.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fully preserves the streaming‐aware PFB parsing patch in both FontBox and PDFBox [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmodules.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Does not touch harness code, tests, or external libraries, in compliance with [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproject guidelines.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Leverages JDK built‐in APIs [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`java.nio.file` and `java.util.Arrays`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m which are [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malready available under the project’s Java [0m[1;36m1.8[0m[39m+ requirement.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No risk of hiding logic errors or altering downstream behaviour beyond fixing the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompilation break.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe codebase experienced a fuzzing-triggered Java OutOfMemoryError inside PDFBox [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhen parsing a Type [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m font [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPFB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m stream. The patch attempt modified [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDType1Font.java` by removing legacy segment-based font creation and adding [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mseveral new imports for streaming-based parsing. After applying the patch, the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuild failed with three “cannot find symbol” errors for `HashMap` and `List`, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating missing imports in `PDType1Font.java`.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fuzzer hit a `FuzzerSecurityIssueLow: Out of memory` exception during PDF text [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextraction.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Stack trace pinpoints `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb` consuming [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexcessive heap, leading to `java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space`.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The failure occurred when PDFBox’s `PDType1Font` loaded a PFB font via [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Type1Font.createWithPFB`, invoked by a PDF text stripper in an example fuzzer [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Edited `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdmodel/font/PDType1Font.java`.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Added imports:  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSName`  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.common.PDStream`  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `org.apache.fontbox.type1.Type1Font`  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `java.io.BufferedInputStream`  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `java.io.ByteArrayOutputStream`  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser`  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Removed the block that calls the legacy `[0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithSegments[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. Comment noted “legacy segment-based creation removed; streaming fallback [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandles segments.”[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No additions were made for `java.util.HashMap` or `java.util.List`, which are [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstill referenced elsewhere in the file.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBuild result after patch  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Maven compilation errors in `PDType1Font.java`:  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Lines referencing `HashMap` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround imports and field definitions[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m now fail due[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto missing `import java.util.HashMap;`  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • A line referencing `List` similarly fails without `import java.util.List;`  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Three “cannot find symbol” errors caused the PDFBox module to fail its [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompilation phase while other modules compiled successfully.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for further investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Review the import section of `PDType1Font.java` to ensure all required Java [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcollections [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`HashMap`, `List`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are imported after patch changes.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inspect other parts of `PDType1Font.java` that depend on segment-based parsing or[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The last patch to `PDType1Font.java` inadvertently removed the imports for [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`java.util.HashMap` and `java.util.List`.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The class still references `HashMap` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfor `ALT_NAMES` and `codeToBytesMap`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand `List` [0m[1;39m([0m[39min `[0m[1;35mgetFontMatrix[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m but lacks the corresponding import statements, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcausing the three “cannot find symbol” compilation errors.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Critical Logic to Preserve  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The streaming-based PFB parsing logic and all newly added imports [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`COSName`, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDStream`, `Type1Font`, `BufferedInputStream`, `ByteArrayOutputStream`, [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PfbParser`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m must remain intact.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Legacy segment-based creation was deliberately removed; do not revert that [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchange.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Fix Steps  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Open `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdmodel/font/PDType1Font.java`. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Locate the import section [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnear the top of the file[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, where you currently [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhave:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import java.util.Arrays;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.common.PDStream;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import org.apache.fontbox.type1.Type1Font;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import java.io.BufferedInputStream;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import java.io.ByteArrayOutputStream;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import java.util.Map;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Immediately after `import java.util.Arrays;`, re-insert the two missing [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimports:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import java.util.HashMap;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      import java.util.List;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Ensure the remaining imports are unchanged [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincluding `java.util.Map` and the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstreaming/PFB parsing imports[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e. Save and recompile. The missing symbol errors for `HashMap` and `List` should[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbe resolved.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Reintroducing the two standard Java collection imports restores the compiler’s[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mability to resolve all `HashMap` and `List` references without affecting any of the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnewly added PFB streaming logic.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This minimal change directly addresses the compilation errors reported, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaintains the existing functionality [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincluding the new streaming fallback[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdoes not alter any test or harness code.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Side Effects and Mitigation  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No functional behavior is changed.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No additional dependencies or broad exception changes are introduced.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Existing tests and fuzz harnesses will continue running as before.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. References  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar import declarations exist in other PDFBox font classes [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDTrueTypeFont.java`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m where `HashMap` and `List` are used; this patch aligns [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDType1Font.java` with those patterns.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
