[2;36m                    [0m         [39m@@ [0m[1;36m-170[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m +[0m[1;36m254[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m86[0m[39m @@[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 throw new [0m[1;35mEOFException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"EOF while reading PFB font"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             total += size;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-            [0m[1;35mtypeList.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecordType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-            [0m[1;35mbarrList.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mar[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+     * Stream-based parsing of PFB format with a total byte limit.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    private void [0m[1;35mparsePfbStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal InputStream in, final long maxTotalBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrows IOException[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        int total = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            int marker = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmarker == [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                break;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmarker != START_MARKER[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Start marker missing"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            int recordType = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecordType == EOF_MARKER[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                break;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecordType != ASCII_MARKER && recordType != BINARY_MARKER[0m[1;39m)[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Incorrect record type: "[0m[39m + recordType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            int size = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            size |= [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            size |= [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            size |= [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m24[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Negative segment size: "[0m[39m + size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            total += size;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtotal > maxTotalBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PFB stream exceeds maximum allowed size: "[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+ total[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m ar = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39msize[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            int offset = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            while [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset < size[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                int r = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[39mar, offset, size - offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mr == [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                offset += r;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecordType == ASCII_MARKER && segment1 == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecordType == BINARY_MARKER && segment2 == null[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                segment2 = ar;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39msegment1 == null || segment2 == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+     * Returns first [0m[1;39m([0m[39mASCII[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m segment as InputStream.[0m                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn out-of-memory error [0m[1;39m([0m[39mFuzzerSecurityIssueLow[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m was reported when processing [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcertain PDF inputs through Apache PDFBox’s text extraction path. The exception [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moriginates in `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb`, indicating an unbounded [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap allocation while parsing PFB [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPrinter Font Binary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m data. A proposed patch [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremoved the legacy segment-based invocation of `Type1Font.createWithSegments` in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDType1Font`, under the assumption that a streaming fallback would suffice. After [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplying the patch, the same OutOfMemoryError still occurs, now with the stack [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrace pointing to the modified `PDType1Font` constructor but ultimately still [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfailing in `PfbParser.parsePfb`.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer entry point `com.example.PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtriggers PDF text extraction via `PDFTextStripper`.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- During font setup, `PDType1Font.<init>` calls into `Type1Font.createWithPFB`, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich instantiates `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser`.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside `PfbParser.parsePfb`, a `java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space` is [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrown when handling certain PFB font data.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Jazzer reports this as `FuzzerSecurityIssueLow`, and suggests using a larger heap[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`-Xmx1710m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to reproduce.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mObservations and Findings  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The heap exhaustion occurs unconditionally within `PfbParser.parsePfb`, not in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclient code.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The issue is reproducible before and after the attempted patch.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack trace consistently shows the failure in font parsing rather than [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdownstream text processing.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- File modified: [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdmodel/font/PDType1Font.java`[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Added duplicate imports for `HashMap` and `List` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno functional effect[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Within the constructor logic handling PFB-based fonts, the block that [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconditionally created a `Type1Font` from two PFB segments was removed:[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```diff[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  -    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength1 > [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m && length2 > [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  -    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  -        t1 = [0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithSegments[0m[1;39m([0m[39msegment1, segment2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Revert the ineffective PDType1Font patch:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Restore the conditional segment-based creation block in `PDType1Font` so that [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mboth the legacy segment path and the streaming fallback remain available. Removing [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis block did not address the real problem [0m[1;39m([0m[39munbounded buffering in the parser[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit must be restored to preserve functionality.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Refactor PfbParser to operate in true streaming mode:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Introduce a new constructor `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream pfbStream, long [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaxSegmentSize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` that drives parsing directly from the provided `InputStream` [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minstead of `byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`.  Remove or deprecate the internal `ByteArrayInputStream` [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffering path.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In the streaming constructor, read only PFB record headers [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstart marker, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecord type, length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and immediately wrap each subsequent segment in a [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`BoundedInputStream` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor custom `SegmentInputStream`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that enforces the declared [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength and prevents overshoot.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Keep track of only two primary segments needed by the Type [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m font parser: the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mASCII segment and the binary segment. Maintain references to these `InputStream` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwrappers without materializing them fully in memory.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Preserve the existing `MAX_LENGTH` and record-size checks; if a segment’s [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength exceeds the configured limit, throw an `IOException` early to prevent OOM.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Extend Type1Font and Type1Parser to accept streaming segments:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Add a new factory method in `Type1Font`:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        public static Type1Font [0m[1;35mcreateWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream pfbStream, long [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaxSegmentSize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      which instantiates `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbStream, maxSegmentSize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, obtains two [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msegment streams [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mgetSegment1Stream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;35mgetSegment2Stream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and delegates to a [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnew `[0m[1;35mType1Parser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream ascii, InputStream binary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Overload `[0m[1;35mType1Parser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to read from the provided `InputStream`s in[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmanageable chunks [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., 8KB buffer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, mirroring the existing parsing logic but [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout requiring whole-segment `byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m` buffers.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Update PDType1FontEmbedder to eliminate full-input buffering:[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replace `byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfbBytes = [0m[1;35mpfbStream.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` and [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        `type1 = [0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbStream, DEFAULT_MAX_SEGMENT_SIZE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This change prevents the initial full read of the PFB stream and ensures [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing stays within the streaming path.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Maintain backward compatibility and fallback:[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Keep the existing `[0m[1;35mcreateWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructors[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mas deprecated fallbacks. They will continue to function for small or legacy fonts [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbut are no longer the default path.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Document the streaming API in the release notes, highlighting the new [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`maxSegmentSize` parameter and the default threshold used to guard against [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexcessive memory usage.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Protect existing tests and harness:[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Do not alter fuzzing harness, test code, or any upstream calls to [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDFTextStripper`. The new streaming path is invoked transparently when [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDType1FontEmbedder` or `PDType1Font` load embedded PFB fonts.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure the legacy code paths remain operational so that existing [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munit/integration tests pass unchanged.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- By switching to a streaming parser, PFB data is consumed in small, bounded chunks[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrather than fully materialized as `byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`, eliminating the root cause of the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munbounded heap allocations and the resulting OOM.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Enforcing a configurable `maxSegmentSize` [0m[1;39m([0m[39malready present as `MAX_LENGTH`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mensures that maliciously large segments trigger an early exception rather than [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexhausting memory.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This approach preserves existing functionality for small fonts via the deprecated[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbyte-array path, while transparently optimizing embedded font loading for large or [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madversarial inputs.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The streaming enhancement is localized to the fontbox and pdfbox font-loading [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode; no harness, testing, or external libraries are modified, preserving the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintegrity of existing tests and fuzz targets.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Potential side effects [0m[1;39m([0m[39mslightly increased parsing I/O overhead[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are minimal [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompared to the benefit of avoiding OOM. Buffer sizes and thresholds can be tuned [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif needed.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA Jazzer fuzzing run on PDFBox’s font parsing code triggered a Java [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mOutOfMemoryError in `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb` when reading a [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcrafted PFB file. To address the unbounded buffering, a patch was proposed that:[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Replaced the byte-array-only parsing in `PfbParser` with streaming constructors [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand a size-limited `parsePfbStream` method,[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Introduced `segment1`[0m[35m/[0m[39m`segment2` fields and accessor streams,[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Updated `Type1Parser` and `PDType1FontEmbedder` to consume those streams instead [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof fully materializing the PFB in memory.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWhen the patch was applied, the build failed in the FontBox module with dozens of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompilation errors in `PfbParser.java` and `Type1Parser.java`, primarily “class, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minterface, or enum expected” and “illegal start of type” messages, indicating [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msyntactic corruption.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m• Fuzzer output:  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - com.code_intelligence.jazzer.api.FuzzerSecurityIssueLow: Out of memory [0m[1;39m([0m[39muse [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m‘-Xmx1710m’ to reproduce[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Caused by: java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Stack trace enters `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb`, then flows [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrough PDFBox’s font loading and text-stripping classes.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m• Key observation: the parser reads entire PFB segments into byte arrays without [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimiting their size, leading to unbounded memory use on malformed or huge inputs.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. In `PfbParser.java`:  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Removed license header block and reinserted only `package` and new `import` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstatements.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added private fields `byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m segment1`, `byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m segment2`.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added two new constructors taking `InputStream` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwith an overload for a [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmax-byte limit[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Split out streaming logic into a private `[0m[1;35mparsePfbStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in, long [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaxTotalBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Kept the original `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` path [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpartially edited[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m alongside the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnew streaming code.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introduced accessor methods `[0m[1;35mgetSegment1Stream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mgetSegment2Stream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. In `Type1Parser.java` and `PDType1FontEmbedder.java`:  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Stripped the old license block and re-added `package` and `import java.io.*;`.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `PDType1FontEmbedder`, replaced  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfbBytes = [0m[1;35mpfbStream.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     PfbParser pfbParser = new [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     type1 = [0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     with  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     PfbParser pfbParser = new [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     Type1Parser parser = new [0m[1;35mType1Parser[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     type1 = [0m[1;35mparser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpfbParser.getSegment1Stream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m167[0m[39m:            int got = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[39mar[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m168[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mgot != size[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m169[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m170[0m[39m:                throw new [0m[1;35mEOFException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"EOF while reading PFB font"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m171[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m172[0m[39m:            total += size;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Font.jav[0m[1;92ma:52[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m60[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m52[0m[39m:    public static Type1Font [0m[1;35mcreateWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream pfbStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m53[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m54[0m[39m:        PfbParser pfb = new [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m55[0m[39m:        Type1Parser parser = new [0m[1;35mType1Parser[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m56[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35mparser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpfb.getSegment1[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m[1;35mpfb.getSegment2[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m57[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m58[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m59[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m60[0m[39m:     * Constructs a new Type1Font object from a .pfb stream.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdmodel/font/PDType1FontEmbedder.jav[0m[1;92ma:60[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m68[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m60[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m61[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m read the pfb[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m62[0m[39m:        byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfbBytes = [0m[1;35mpfbStream.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m63[0m[39m:        PfbParser pfbParser = new [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m64[0m[39m:        type1 = [0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m65[0m[39m:        [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m66[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mencoding == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m67[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m68[0m[39m:            fontEncoding = [0m[1;35mType1Encoding.fromFontBox[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtype1.getEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.jav[0m[1;92ma:58[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m60[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m58[0m[39m:    public Type1Font [0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m segment1, byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m segment2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m59[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m60[0m[39m:        font = new [0m[1;35mType1Font[0m[1;39m([0m[39msegment1, segment2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Restore file headers and correct misplaced comment text  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In PfbParser.java, Type1Parser.java, and PDType1FontEmbedder.java, revert the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheader removals that dropped the opening `[0m[35m/[0m[39m*` or closing `*[0m[35m/[0m[39m`. Either fully [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserve the original ASF license block [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecommended[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or remove it entirely, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mensuring that no stray `*` lines remain outside a comment.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure the package declaration is the first non-comment token, followed by [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimport statements, then class-level Javadoc.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Consolidate and rebalance braces in PfbParser.java  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove the old `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructor that calls [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, and also remove the `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString filename[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverload.  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Keep only:  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: retains backward compatibility and calls a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munified parsing method.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream pfbStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpfbStream, long maxTotalBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: streaming constructors.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Refactor the two parsing routines into one of these approaches:  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Have the byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m constructor wrap its array in a `ByteArrayInputStream` and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcall `[0m[1;35mparsePfbStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39min, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, eliminating `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` entirely.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Or keep both `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mparsePfbStream[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, but ensure they [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshare identical logic for reading the three segments and enforce `MAX_LENGTH`; [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremove the duplicated code blocks and merge them cleanly.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Declare only one set of private fields [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m segment1`, `byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m segment2`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand drop any unused array fields such as `pfbdata` or `lengths` if they’re no [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlonger referenced.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Verify that every opening brace has its matching closing brace, and that [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethods are not inadvertently nested or left open.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Add streaming overload to Type1Parser  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.java`, fix the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheader, then inside the class add:  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      * Parses a Type1 font from separate PFB segments.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     public Type1Font [0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream asciiSegment, InputStream binarySegment[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m seg1 = [0m[1;35masciiSegment.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m safe: segments limited by [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPfbParser.MAX_LENGTH[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m seg2 = [0m[1;35mbinarySegment.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return [0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[39mseg1, seg2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Keep the existing `[0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m, byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method intact for backwards [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompatibility.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Update PDType1FontEmbedder to use streaming PfbParser  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdmodel/font/PDType1FontEmbedder.java`, fix[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe header, then replace the block:  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfbBytes = [0m[1;35mpfbStream.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     PfbParser pfbParser = new [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     type1 = [0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     with  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     PfbParser pfbParser = new [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfbStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     Type1Parser parser = new [0m[1;35mType1Parser[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     type1 = [0m[1;35mparser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mpfbParser.getSegment1Stream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mpfbParser.getSegment2Stream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove any stray calls to `[0m[1;35mreadAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on the full PFB stream and drop the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munused local `pfbBytes` variable.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Ensure consistent MAX_LENGTH enforcement and segment ordering  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Verify that `parsePfbStream` enforces `maxTotalBytes` on the cumulative [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msegment sizes and that it assigns the first ASCII marker block to `segment1` and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe first BINARY block to `segment2`.  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Optionally, unify the two parsing methods so that the byte-array path reuses [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe streaming logic, preventing future drift.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Validate formatting, imports, and compile  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run `mvn compile` on the `fontbox` module to confirm no syntax errors.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure that no tests or harness code have been modified.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mExplanation of approach  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The compilation errors “class, interface, or enum expected” were caused by broken[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomment blocks and duplicated, unbalanced code introduced by an incomplete patch. [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy fully restoring or cleanly removing the license headers and reapplying [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimport/package ordering, we eliminate stray tokens.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Consolidating parsing logic avoids duplicated code and potential brace [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmismatches. Exposing both byte-array and streaming constructors keeps API [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompatibility while preventing OOM by never buffering the entire font in one go.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Adding a streaming `[0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream, InputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to Type1Parser and updating [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe embedder removes double buffering and honors the same fuzzer entry points [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout touching harness code.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This strategy preserves existing functionality [0m[1;39m([0m[39mold constructors and parse [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethods remain[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and applies strict size limits only in production code. Potential [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mside effects are minimal; the only additional memory is for the two segments whose [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotal size is capped, mitigating the original OOM root cause.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
